{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs","description":"Adds accessibility.js snippet to all renderered pages","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","accessibility","a11y"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"alampros","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/5f861ff7bbddb5c7a7a9285b507eb4e6"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/alampros/gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs</h1>\n<p>Adds Github’s <a href=\"https://github.com/github/accessibilityjs\">accessibility.js</a> snippet to all rendered pages.</p>\n<p><img src=\".github/gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs-screenshot.png\" alt=\"screenshot\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Options</h2>\n<p>Defaults: </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      injectStyles<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\n        .accessibility-error {\n          border: 3px solid #f00;\n        }\n      `</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      errorClassName<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`accessibility-error`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      onError<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// do something with the error</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h3 id=\"fancier-styles\"><a href=\"#fancier-styles\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Fancier Styles</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      injectStyles<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\n        .accessibility-error {\n          box-shadow: 0 0 3px 1px #f00;\n          background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.25);\n          position: relative;\n        }\n        .accessibility-error:before {\n          content: \"A11Y\";\n          position: absolute;\n          top: 0;\n          left: 0;\n          color: #fff;\n          font-size: 10px;\n          background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);\n          transform: translateY(-100%);\n        }\n      `</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h3 id=\"just-logging\"><a href=\"#just-logging\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Just Logging</h3>\n<p>Don’t modify the DOM at all, just log errors with the default <code class=\"language-text\">onError</code> logger.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      injectStyles<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      errorClassName<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n      </div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-accessibilityjs/","id":"f259f8c5-e837-5b8e-8de8-2650fea0d4db"}}